      "text": "：Attach to RenderMan PxrDomeLight（连接到 RenderMan PxrDomeLight）",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:8",
      "text": "Overview（资源概览）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:9",
      "text": "借助这个 Stylized Environment Light Library，你可以在 RenderMan 的 Preset Browser 中使用一些 realistic、psychedelic 和 stylized HDRI。",
      "ascii_letters": 85,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:13",
      "text": "Stylized",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:14",
      "text": "folder 放入你的 RenderMan Asset Library",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:15",
      "text": "EnvironmentMaps",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:16",
      "text": "folder。建议将安装默认的 RenderManAssetLibrary folder 转移到非安装目录中、且具有 full writing privileges 的位置。",
      "ascii_letters": 54,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:17",
      "text": "当你转移 Materials folder 并把 Asset Library 移到其他位置后，必须通过 Maya preferences 告诉 Maya 使用新的 path。",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:18",
      "text": "你的 preset browser 会显示所有 new presets，包括我们的新",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:19",
      "text": "Stylized",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ff35d24867:20",
      "text": "Env Lights，无需重启 Maya。你可能需要关闭并重新打开 Preset Browser 来 refresh。",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
